ask Contract","title":"Gate determinista de rule contracts"}},{"id":"contracts/rules-gate.md#38","metadata":{"content":"n >=1 ERROR.","okf_concept":"contracts/rules-gate.md","okf_type":"Task Contract","title":"Gate determinista de rule contracts"}},{"id":"contracts/rules-gate.md#39","metadata":{"content":">=1 ERROR.","okf_concept":"contracts/rules-gate.md","okf_type":"Task Contract","title":"Gate determinista de rule contracts"}},{"id":"contracts/rules-gate.md#4","metadata":{"content":"so capa-opcional, con INFO) - 1 con >=1 ERROR.","okf_concept":"contracts/rules-gate.md","okf_type":"Task Contract","title":"Gate determinista de rule contracts"}},{"id":"contracts/rules-gate.md#40","metadata":{"content":">=1 ERROR.","okf_concept":"contracts/rules-gate.md","okf_type":"Task Contract","title":"Gate determinista de rule contracts"}},{"id":"contracts/rules-gate.md#41","metadata":{"content":"=1 ERROR.","okf_concept":"contracts/rules-gate.md","okf_type":"Task Contract","title":"Gate determinista de rule contracts"}},{"id":"contracts/rules-gate.md#42","metadata":{"content":"1 ERROR.","okf_concept":"contracts/rules-gate.md","okf_type":"Task Contract","title":"Gate determinista de rule contracts"}},{"id":"contracts/rules-gate.md#43","metadata":{"content":"ERROR.","okf_concept":"contracts/rules-gate.md","okf_type":"Task Contract","title":"Gate determinista de rule contracts"}},{"id":"contracts/rules-gate.md#44","metadata":{"content":"ERROR.","okf_concept":"contracts/rules-gate.md","okf_type":"Task Contract","title":"Gate determinista de rule contracts"}},{"id":"contracts/rules-gate.md#45","metadata":{"content":"RROR.","okf_concept":"contracts/rules-gate.md","okf_type":"Task Contract","title":"Gate determinista de rule contracts"}},{"id":"contracts/rules-gate.md#46","metadata":{"content":"ROR.","okf_concept":"contracts/rules-gate.md","okf_type":"Task Contract","title":"Gate determinista de rule contracts"}},{"id":"contracts/rules-gate.md#47","metadata":{"content":"OR.","okf_concept":"contracts/rules-gate.md","okf_type":"Task Contract","title":"Gate determinista de rule contracts"}},{"id":"contracts/rules-gate.md#48","metadata":{"content":"R.","okf_concept":"contracts/rules-gate.md","okf_type":"Task Contract","title":"Gate determinista de rule contracts"}},{"id":"contracts/rules-gate.md#49","metadata":{"content":".","okf_concept":"contracts/rules-gate.md","okf_type":"Task Contract","title":"Gate determinista de rule contracts"}},{"id":"contracts/rules-gate.md#5","metadata":{"content":"o capa-opcional, con INFO) - 1 con >=1 ERROR.","okf_concept":"contracts/rules-gate.md","okf_type":"Task Contract","title":"Gate determinista de rule contracts"}},{"id":"contracts/rules-gate.md#50","metadata":{"content":"## Invariants\n- Reglas y semantica EXACTAS del docstring del oraculo congelado: `JSON`, `FAMILIA`\n  (top-level fuera de _comment + 7 familias + code_only + golden), `GOLDEN`,\n  `GOLDEN_FROZEN` (sha256 LF-normalizado, mismo algoritmo que tests_sha256; msg con\n  esperado y actual), `GOLDEN_FORMA`, `CODE_ONLY` (reason no vacia), `REPRO`\n  (rule_engine.evaluate reproduce violations - code_only_miss por campo top-level,\n  nombrando el caso divergente).\n- El gate importa SOLO `rule_engine` (motor declarativo); JAMAS el validador de codigo de\n  ningun dominio (los oraculos son independientes).\n- Escanea SOLO `*.rules.json`; otros .json se ignoran.","okf_concept":"contracts/rules-gate.md","okf_type":"Task Contract","title":"Gate determinista de rule contracts"}},{"id":"contracts/rules-gate.md#51","metadata":{"content":"anea SOLO `*.rules.json`; otros .json se ignoran. `golden.path` relativo al rule-set.\n- Capa opcional: dir ausente o sin rule-sets -> findings vacios; el CLI lo anuncia (INFO).\n- Determinista: findings ordenados (archivo, regla), estables entre corridas; stdlib puro;\n  sin red; sin subprocess; sin LLM; mensajes ASCII.\n\n## Examples\n- Par rule-set+golden valido y sellado -> `[]` y CLI exit 0.\n- Clave top-level `requird` (typo) -> ERROR `FAMILIA` nombrandola.\n- Golden editado sin re-sellar -> ERROR `GOLDEN_FROZEN` con ambos hashes.\n- Rule-set al que le falta una regla que el golden espera -> ERROR `REPRO` nombrando el caso.\n- Directorio vacio o inexistente -> exit 0 con INFO (post-init verde).","okf_concept":"contracts/rules-gate.md","okf_type":"Task Contract","title":"Gate determinista de rule contracts"}},{"id":"contracts/rules-gate.md#52","metadata":{"content":"nexistente -> exit 0 con INFO (post-init verde).\n\n## Do / Don't\n- DO: espejar interfaz, formato de salida y estilo de `scripts/validate_okf.py`.\n- DO: mensajes con archivo + regla + causa exacta; el de GOLDEN_FROZEN nombra el comando\n  de sellado (`python scripts/validate_contracts.py --hash <golden>`).\n- DON'T: red, subprocess, dependencias fuera de stdlib; importar validadores de dominio;\n  ejecutar `code_only`; tocar rule_engine.py, su oraculo, el ejemplo de pagos o el CI.\n\n## Tests\n(Los tests estan en `tests/test_validate_rules.py`, autorados por el orquestador y\ncongelados por `tests_sha256`: el implementador no los escribe ni los modifica. Fixtures\nen tempdir para cada regla + capa opcional + determinismo + ejemplo real del repo + CLI.)","okf_concept":"contracts/rules-gate.md","okf_type":"Task Contract","title":"Gate determinista de rule contracts"}},{"id":"contracts/rules-gate.md#53","metadata":{"content":"l + determinismo + ejemplo real del repo + CLI.)\n\n## Constraints\n- PARAR y reportar si... reproducir el golden exigiera importar el validador de codigo de\n  un dominio, o si el oraculo congelado fuera internamente contradictorio.","okf_concept":"contracts/rules-gate.md","okf_type":"Task Contract","title":"Gate determinista de rule contracts"}},{"id":"contracts/rules-gate.md#6","metadata":{"content":"capa-opcional, con INFO) - 1 con >=1 ERROR.","okf_concept":"contracts/rules-gate.md","okf_type":"Task Contract","title":"Gate determinista de rule contracts"}},{"id":"contracts/rules-gate.md#7","metadata":{"content":"capa-opcional, con INFO) - 1 con >=1 ERROR.","okf_concept":"contracts/rules-gate.md","okf_type":"Task Contract","title":"Gate determinista de rule contracts"}},{"id":"contracts/rules-gate.md#8","metadata":{"content":"apa-opcional, con INFO) - 1 con >=1 ERROR.","okf_concept":"contracts/rules-gate.md","okf_type":"Task Contract","title":"Gate determinista de rule contracts"}},{"id":"contracts/rules-gate.md#9","metadata":{"content":"pa-opcional, con INFO) - 1 con >=1 ERROR.","okf_concept":"contracts/rules-gate.md","okf_type":"Task Contract","title":"Gate determinista de rule contracts"}},{"id":"contracts/sample_task.md#0","metadata":{"content":"# Contract: Hello World\n\n## Intent\nImplementar una función que retorne un saludo simple. Se alinea con nuestra meta de desarrollo demostrada en [la arquitectura general](../index.md).\n\n## Interface\n```python\ndef hello(name: str) -> str:\n    ...\n```\n\n## Invariants\n- La función no lanza excepciones.\n\n## Examples\n- `hello(\"Agente\")` -> `\"Hello, Agente\"`\n- `hello(\"Mundo\")` -> `\"Hello, Mundo\"`\n- `hello(\"\")` -> `\"Hello, \"`\n\n## Do / Don't\n- DO: Usar f-strings de Python.\n\n## Tests\n(Los tests están en `tests/test_sample.py`)\n\n## Constraints\n- PARAR y reportar si... necesitas conectarte a la red.","okf_concept":"contracts/sample_task.md","okf_type":"Task Contract","title":"Ejemplo de Tarea (Hello World)"}},{"id":"contracts/skills-gate.md#0","metadata":{"content":"# Contract: Gate de skills (validate_skills)\n\n## Intent\nImplementar `scripts/validate_skills.py`: el gate de nivel 1 que valida las\nskills de agente del repo (`skills/` y `.agents/skills`) — estructura,\nfrontmatter, cuerpo, enlaces y unicidad de nombres. Es INFRAESTRUCTURA:\ncustodia activos reales, no ejemplos. Spec: `specs/CONTRACT-24-skills-gate.md`.","okf_concept":"contracts/skills-gate.md","okf_type":"Task Contract","title":"Gate de skills de agente"}},{"id":"contracts/skills-gate.md#1","metadata":{"content":"mplos. Spec: `specs/CONTRACT-24-skills-gate.md`.","okf_concept":"contracts/skills-gate.md","okf_type":"Task Contract","title":"Gate de skills de agente"}},{"id":"contracts/skills-gate.md#10","metadata":{"content":"ec: `specs/CONTRACT-24-skills-gate.md`.","okf_concept":"contracts/skills-gate.md","okf_type":"Task Contract","title":"Gate de skills de agente"}},{"id":"contracts/skills-gate.md#11","metadata":{"content":"c: `specs/CONTRACT-24-skills-gate.md`.","okf_concept":"contracts/skills-gate.md","okf_type":"Task Contract","title":"Gate de skills de agente"}},{"id":"contracts/skills-gate.md#12","metadata":{"content":": `specs/CONTRACT-24-skills-gate.md`.","okf_concept":"contracts/skills-gate.md","okf_type":"Task Contract","title":"Gate de skills de agente"}},{"id":"contracts/skills-gate.md#13","metadata":{"content":"`specs/CONTRACT-24-skills-gate.md`.","okf_concept":"contracts/skills-gate.md","okf_type":"Task Contract","title":"Gate de skills de agente"}},{"id":"contracts/skills-gate.md#14","metadata":{"content":"`specs/CONTRACT-24-skills-gate.md`.","okf_concept":"contracts/skills-gate.md","okf_type":"Task Contract","title":"Gate de skills de agente"}},{"id":"contracts/skills-gate.md#15","metadata":{"content":"specs/CONTRACT-24-skills-gate.md`.","okf_concept":"contracts/skills-gate.md","okf_type":"Task Contract","title":"Gate de skills de agente"}},{"id":"contracts/skills-gate.md#16","metadata":{"content":"pecs/CONTRACT-24-skills-gate.md`.","okf_concept":"contracts/skills-gate.md","okf_type":"Task Contract","title":"Gate de skills de agente"}},{"id":"contracts/skills-gate.md#17","metadata":{"content":"ecs/CONTRACT-24-skills-gate.md`.","okf_concept":"contracts/skills-gate.md","okf_type":"Task Contract","title":"Gate de skills de agente"}},{"id":"contracts/skills-gate.md#18","metadata":{"content":"cs/CONTRACT-24-skills-gate.md`.","okf_concept":"contracts/skills-gate.md","okf_type":"Task Contract","title":"Gate de skills de agente"}},{"id":"contracts/skills-gate.md#19","metadata":