rder_rules.md","okf_type":"Data Model","title":"Reglas de control de fronteras"}},{"id":"data_models/border_rules.md#5","metadata":{"content":"KF).\n\n## El record: una solicitud de entrada","okf_concept":"data_models/border_rules.md","okf_type":"Data Model","title":"Reglas de control de fronteras"}},{"id":"data_models/border_rules.md#50","metadata":{"content":"; debe COINCIDIR con `applicant_name` (frontera). |\n| `doc.expiry_year` | number  | `>=` el año de politica (documento no vencido).              |\n| `applicant_name`  | string  | Obligatorio.                                                 |\n\n## Mapeo vocabulario papers-please -> familias declarativas","okf_concept":"data_models/border_rules.md","okf_type":"Data Model","title":"Reglas de control de fronteras"}},{"id":"data_models/border_rules.md#51","metadata":{"content":"cabulario papers-please -> familias declarativas","okf_concept":"data_models/border_rules.md","okf_type":"Data Model","title":"Reglas de control de fronteras"}},{"id":"data_models/border_rules.md#52","metadata":{"content":"abulario papers-please -> familias declarativas","okf_concept":"data_models/border_rules.md","okf_type":"Data Model","title":"Reglas de control de fronteras"}},{"id":"data_models/border_rules.md#53","metadata":{"content":"bulario papers-please -> familias declarativas","okf_concept":"data_models/border_rules.md","okf_type":"Data Model","title":"Reglas de control de fronteras"}},{"id":"data_models/border_rules.md#54","metadata":{"content":"ulario papers-please -> familias declarativas","okf_concept":"data_models/border_rules.md","okf_type":"Data Model","title":"Reglas de control de fronteras"}},{"id":"data_models/border_rules.md#55","metadata":{"content":"lario papers-please -> familias declarativas","okf_concept":"data_models/border_rules.md","okf_type":"Data Model","title":"Reglas de control de fronteras"}},{"id":"data_models/border_rules.md#56","metadata":{"content":"ario papers-please -> familias declarativas","okf_